<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>EMA616_07_SU_0008_s</title>

        <!-- 공통 js-->
        <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

        <!-- 공통 css-->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema616_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_07_su_0008">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6">
            <div>
                <span lang="y">두 직육면체 모양 상자 중 어느 상자의 겉넓이가 몇 ㎠ 더 넓은지 구해 봅시다.</span>
                <button type="button" class="btn calculator">계산기</button>
            </div>
        </h2>
      </section>
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">두 상자 가와 나의 겉넓이는 각각 몇 ㎠인가요?</h3>
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="box_a">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_07_SU/box_1.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="unit_a">12 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_b">25 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_c">15 ㎝</div>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field
                  type="number"
                  data-answer-single="1710"
                  text-align="center"
                ></math-field>
                <span>㎠</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box_b">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_07_SU/box_2.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="unit_a">30 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_b">30 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_c">6 ㎝</div>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field
                  type="number"
                  data-answer-single="2520"
                  text-align="center"
                ></math-field>
                <span>㎠</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">어느 상자의 겉넓이가 몇 ㎠ 더 넓은지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="box_a">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_07_SU/box_1.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="unit_a">12 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_b">25 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_c">15 ㎝</div>
            </div>
            <div class="box_b">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_07_SU/box_2.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="unit_a">30 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_b">30 ㎝</div>
              <div class="unit_c">6 ㎝</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="answer_area">
            <div class="dropdown_wrap">
              <select class="custom_dropdown" data-answer-single="나">
                <option></option>
                <!--최초선택데이터 생성 방지용-->
                <option value="가"></option>
                <option value="나"></option>
              </select>
              <span>상자의 겉넓이가</span>
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field
                  type="number"
                  data-answer-single="810"
                  text-align="center"
                ></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>㎠ 더 넓습니다.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
